name: Wild Country Rock Set 1-10
description: Operating on the original curved-face principle, the convex side locks the nut into place against the 2 contact point of the concave side, creating a stable wedged placement. Side tapers assist in wedging in sideways placements. The transverse taper provides more bite in slightly flared placements.Colour-coded anodized heads for quick selection.6064 aluminum with steel cables.Includes Wild Country Rocks sizes 1 to 10.
